###
# Video Extractor API - MVP Simplificado
# Solo encolamiento de tareas
###

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@callbackUrl = https://webhook.site/tu-url-aqui

### 1. Encolar extracción básica de thumbnails
POST {{baseUrl}}/video-extractor/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "https://sample-videos.com/zip/10/mp4/SampleVideo_720x480_1mb.mp4",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}"
}

###

### 2. Extracción con opciones personalizadas
POST {{baseUrl}}/video-extractor/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "https://sample-videos.com/zip/10/mp4/SampleVideo_720x480_1mb.mp4",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}",
  "requestId": "custom-extraction-001",
  "metadata": {
    "category": "sample-video",
    "source": "sample-videos.com",
    "user": "test-user"
  },
  "options": {
    "fps": 0.5,
    "width": 640,
    "height": 480,
    "format": "png"
  }
}

###

### 3. Prueba de validación - FPS fuera de rango
POST {{baseUrl}}/video-extractor/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "https://sample-videos.com/zip/10/mp4/SampleVideo_720x480_1mb.mp4",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}",
  "options": {
    "fps": 50.0
  }
}

###

### 4. Prueba de error - URL inválida
POST {{baseUrl}}/video-extractor/enqueue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "https://invalid-url-for-testing.com/nonexistent.mp4",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}",
  "requestId": "error-test"
}

###
